data.description: Less than a half mile away from Costco, and the Prasada shopping center. This Gorgeous model home has extensive upgrades that include wood floors as you enter the home. Office/den with french doors located on the first floor. Large kitchen with pantry. Upgraded counters, and tile floors that opens to a large family room. The home also features a formal living and dinning room. Second floor has a loft area with bedrooms. Master is large with generous master bath with separate shower and bath, large walk in closet. Backyard features a refreshing pool with water fall and covered patio.
